title: Anyone Else spectate not working or is it just me.

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

replies.body: There appears to be an issue with spectating atm, it's been passed on and should hopefully get fixed up soon :)
The clubs outage isn't OCE specific and is tracked here: http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/dtJNLo9r-clubs-outage-oct-2016
I also noticed that spectate doesn't show you the real time live spectate but rather has like a 5-10 min delay.
Spectate has always had a 3min delay, it's to stop people spectating friends in ranked and say, telling them where the enemy team is.
